OL,3,CAndy Burnham promises to 'bring back
OL,4,Chope' as he becomes Labour Leader
OL,6,FAndy Burnham has officially become
OL,7,FLeader of the Labour Party ahead of
OL,8,Fhis entry into No 10 as prime minister
OL,9,Fon Monday.
OL,11,FThe former Greater Manchester mayor
OL,12,Freturned to Westminster in June as the
OL,13,FMP for Makerfield, leading to the
OL,14,Fresignation of Sir Keir Starmer as
OL,15,Fparty leader and subsequently prime
OL,16,Fminister.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
