OL,3,CAndy Burnham promises to 'bring back
OL,4,Chope' as he becomes Labour Leader
OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FSpeaking at the event, the new leader
OL,12,Fpromised to "bring back hope" as he
OL,13,Fboldly claimed his leadership "is the
OL,14,Fmost significant change moment in our
OL,15,Fpolitics for 40 years".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
