CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1784387896
OL,3,CAndy Burnham promises to 'bring back
OL,4,Chope' as he becomes Labour Leader
OL,6,FHe claimed that Britain took "a series
OL,7,Fof wrong turns in the 1980s" when
OL,8,F"political power was centralised and
OL,9,Feconomic power privatised" as he set
OL,10,Fout his "five things to make us
OL,11,Fbetter".
OL,13,FThe first of his promises were to
OL,14,Fchange the culture within his party,
OL,15,Fending the "insidious briefing
OL,16,Fculture" and working towards a "united
OL,17,FLabour Party", claiming he will "set a
OL,18,Fdirection that is distinctively
OL,19,FLabour".
OL,26,@nD@^OUoD@\O]pD@AOUqD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
