CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1784387896
OL,3,CAndy Burnham promises to 'bring back
OL,4,Chope' as he becomes Labour Leader
OL,6,FHe said: "We won't try to out-Green
OL,7,Fthe Greens. Or out-Reform, Reform."
OL,9,FHe went on to set out his ideas to
OL,10,Fchange politics, change the direction
OL,11,Fof the party, take politics out of
OL,12,FWestminster and taking power back to
OL,13,Fpeople.
OL,15,FBurnham said that he "will work to
OL,16,Fbuild a new politics" and said "we
OL,17,Fmight enjoy point scoring against
OL,18,Fother. The public don't" and promised
OL,19,Fto fix the big things instead.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
