PN,31306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1784387896
OL,3,CAndy Burnham promises to 'bring back
OL,4,Chope' as he becomes Labour Leader
OL,6,FDeputy Leader Lucy Powell opened the
OL,7,Fconference paying tribute to Starmer's
OL,8,Flegacy calling him the "guy who helped
OL,9,Fsave the Labour Party" and said he was
OL,10,F"solid and steadfast".
OL,12,FShe quickly moved onto the new leader
OL,13,Fsaying under his leadership "we can
OL,14,Fchange people's lives for the better"
OL,15,Fand "restore faith in politics".
OL,17,FBurnham will officially become the
OL,18,FPrime Minster on Monday, when Starmer
OL,19,Fwill speak to the King to resign,
OL,20,Fpaving way for him.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
