PN,31307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1784387896
OL,3,CAndy Burnham promises to 'bring back
OL,4,Chope' as he becomes Labour Leader
OL,6,FHe will become the seventh UK prime
OL,7,Fminister in a decade and at a time
OL,8,Fwhen his party is battling against the
OL,9,Frise in popularity of Reform UK, with
OL,10,Fhis supporters hoping his presence
OL,11,Fwill improve their reputation.
OL,13,FStarmer has said he thinks Labour can
OL,14,Fwin the next election under Burnham
OL,15,Fand said he is "proud to hand over the
OL,16,Fparty in good shape".
OL,18,FAt his final PMQs on Wednesday,
OL,19,FStarmer defended his record and said
OL,20,Fhe was proud "to leave this country in
OL,21,Fa better shape than I found it".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
